se-fails-first`).\n\nSolves the reproduction in\nhttps://github.com/sveltejs/svelte/issues/18221#issuecomment-4507803845","tree":{"sha":"8d0ea682e89b491be156f32c16778a80faf6da35","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/svelte/git/trees/8d0ea682e89b491be156f32c16778a80faf6da35"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/svelte/git/commits/078f901f611237d4c6fed16ef894f33572f9ccba","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqD06BCRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAK/8QAB2jxeIOr0cmeq+6ecThZOyN\npyoWZLDo88nSa5W9S/wR+Tpy9O9Po5q1w7h4cFa1w4CHIDkM9tEy3sKqx72eLQwY\ngZhNeZdCFcr9NDGLWPtc7rRn0r47UotHl7EfKOHKiwwRBGqv7/Sv2eJG3Hl/Kz3h\njPuL3zRlVbKTFv8gP35vdhd3jA4E7FFcf5N6rhN6mzr/qPF5CmVmR/rTznflWTof\nlU2fvrXc/mmlfVCb22glHEUhT1Rzus3ckNXPOqAkd1IJEJMShFvw4myxL4EG5rmM\nQ/FcGSEXrYDF6CRUVhAqKfNTh4ryolzeVYfeNFjHGzDVdmdrncgLdRfopdigBzcX\nVC2sMMOXfUvCqowbTE7d4QCsfmkE4lDuRr18XgYFk4rkv7fPcNmk2C+zXKnARWLM\nwrGuYDf39TWGtxb9IHZncR9LURU2B1fNq8WxRPI7Tc5y2Cinw5Trftzir4+yYh51\nnPnSr2+Ml/00wlES+gnX0LQD7ULP3z7VG7w9uYNKNZV2hvNJ84z7CymZV9GAYqsU\nIN9wpeJxj5N95TOTBJLfiTU9+xD29xWVzFXAYw5Kjhtfa7Qo3BwZIBZra8vjGMEz\nrJC29nEQp6jFrMQhDccDR9ZLMgjXx9leK1+7H0kjhLWxmmPb/2LuePX/8q8uhqhW\n7AUrMjkGkKjmzoNwc9Lp\n=FE+2\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n","payload":"tree 8d0ea682e89b491be156f32c16778a80faf6da35\nparent a6002b587c9d2f40fe2dc48391c372360abbaf0f\nauthor Simon H <5968653+dummdidumm@users.noreply.github.com> 1779388033 +0200\ncommitter GitHub <noreply@github.com> 1779388033 +0200\n\nfix: catch rejected promises while merging/committing (#18266)\n\nA committing/merging batch can have promises that were rejected (e.g. as\nobsolete). We gotta \"forward\" this rejection, too, instead of just the\nsuccessful promise. At best it results in a uncaught rejection\n(`async-branch-merge-obsolete`), at worst it means error boundaries are\nnot correctly displayed (`async-later-promise-fails-first`).\n\nSolves the reproduction in\nhttps://github.com/svelt