inter (#18206)\n\n`SvelteBody` was missing from the visitor map, causing a crash with\n`Error: Not implemented: SvelteBody`. Added the handler (same one-liner\npattern as `SvelteDocument`, `SvelteHead`, etc.) and added `SvelteBody`\nto the `is_block_element` check so whitespace is handled consistently.\n\n### Fix 2: Keyframe percent stops print as `0%%` (#18207)\n\n`Percentage.value` already includes the `%` sign (captured by\n`/\\d+(\\.\\d+)?%/y`), but the printer was writing `` `${node.value}%` `` —\nappending a second `%`. Changed to `context.write(node.value)` to match\nthe `Nth` printer pattern directly above it.\n\nAlso updated the existing `style` snapshot which had `50%%` (the bug was\nsilently baked in), and added dedicated test samples for both fixes.","tree":{"sha":"1710768112282fa78db061d7c7659c483d70f3aa","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/svelte/git/trees/1710768112282fa78db061d7c7659c483d70f3aa"},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sveltejs/svelte/git/commits/ca3f35bf7d3eeea6d0b5f477d208c3fd9c19988c","comment_count":0,"verification":{"verified":true,"reason":"valid","signature":"-----BEGIN PGP SIGNATURE-----\n\nwsFcBAABCAAQBQJqCzY3CRC1aQ7uu5UhlAAAp3QQALA9Rl6Jt0isK3k2pfkfOCZJ\nIm4DMuhVf196kLwZFZVrvoiRoePRpExHImjXUhVn6Zncudvu4RTawTRMEisV2ffS\nZuQSQZGErVb9+PLrxXIObxK9CniugdXNBlWW3xBlQ7zc19aQ25Y6HT1mKnJbnG5w\nq9BrnKSx858ckKU2Eg25iayvmAbJiuLhs7/Rhs1dxkKJJTA5YaaUKDFbcXUhACIA\n8uBOgo2d3y4Fi1v+eZEztdEwjCJVEJG8BpDUmNcPibe7foFGold7B/UZ2VZHSlXr\n8LqRg+9XhVtuskmGqOZFHuUDdJqwJf2i8iHEe1D39Hr5LJWpnBkw4lc+7J2H+ASp\nZ+NBUA31PDXFbf9C18esVVffe1HqbvX00xeCSTQQYmzdxu1uugrcAEBCqV8gm0pr\nSkPeROdmVfMb7t1rlDlIvB22ImWz8j+W6kVXQs0p5VKutvo6Iw4nvHnhCU4r4bW3\nCO22I+KtTpJkO9FQhOits7XmrXvkbbLc3DETSo+7/W/5NVBfNRJrC1GVu7+z5Qy5\nyJhjDvF6IzYtnVDBYF03eLnbm4lvVIc3qzF8Li32Fmgr8XcNOY9sH26VOdZpNIlg\n2Db/Rp17/SpB5FlaMOgtLC0Ld8XWqGJQDxGz1qzVf6M/KQe1RljqgY4RxZFLCbQL\njKD/mR0CYlT5d1Ayik1W\n=bh27\n-----END PGP SIGNATURE-----\n","payload":"tree 1710768112282fa78db061d7c7659c483d70f3aa\npa